2025-10-10HC, TBFinancial Administration ActRemission Order in Respect of Canadian Dental Care Plan Eligibility IssuesRemission Order in Respect of Canadian Dental Care Plan (CDCP) Eligibility Issues in order to (1) remit to any individual who was erroneously found to be eligible for coverage, or subject to an inaccurate co payment tier determination, as a result of the adjusted family net income error, and who received dental care services, an amount equivalent to the erroneous amount paid to dental care providers by the CDCP for such services; (2) remit to any individual who applied for coverage before May 1, 2024, was found to be eligible for coverage and received dental care services, and was subsequently found to be ineligible due to their access to dental insurance, an amount equivalent to the erroneous amount paid to dental care providers by the CDCP for such services.N/A
subject: Remission Order in Respect of Canadian Dental Care Plan Eligibility Issues
precis: Remission Order in Respect of Canadian Dental Care Plan (CDCP) Eligibility Issues in order to (1) remit to any individual who was erroneously found to be eligible for coverage, or subject to an inaccurate co payment tier determination, as a result of the adjusted family net income error, and who received dental care services, an amount equivalent to the erroneous amount paid to dental care providers by the CDCP for such services; (2) remit to any individual who applied for coverage before May 1, 2024, was found to be eligible for coverage and received dental care services, and was subsequently found to be ineligible due to their access to dental insurance, an amount equivalent to the erroneous amount paid to dental care providers by the CDCP for such services.
